{"tid":691884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★朋友探監見笑面 轉述游蕙禎籲勿擔心歡迎來信","createTime":"2018-06-06T06:41:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-06T07:03:21.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c9e3c4098a5f4d6acb371fc806373bb3b716e195","tid":691884,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T06:41:20.000Z","msg":"游的友人Matthew Lam在facebook出post，指昨已經前往監獄探望游，「她的情況良好，精神飽滿，交談中仍見笑面，她寄望各位<span style=\"color: red;\">不用擔心她的獄中生活</span>」。<br />\n<br />\nMatthew Lam在fb表示，游會有信件寄出，告知大家她的狀況；游亦歡迎各位朋友寫信給她，他本人及星火同盟會收集信件，並附上電郵地址及郵寄地址，要求信封註明「游蕙禎收」。有關訊息亦有人代為轉貼在游的fb。<br />\n據了解，由於游所犯的罪行輕微，刑期僅4周兼屬初犯，會被安排羅湖懲教所服刑。不過，游實際刑期不超過1個月，未能按照《監獄條例》第69條因勤奮及行為良好而獲扣減刑期。消息指，游在監獄的生活會如一般囚犯一樣，早上6時15分起身梳洗及清潔囚倉，7時半輪流食早餐，9時工作；女囚犯不會被強制剪髮，游的一頭招牌秀髮可保留，不用捱剪，一般只要紮起頭髮，乾淨企理就可以。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180606/58283141\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180606%2F58283141&d=iSVeGoN7CwIAGDQczWzVlwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=b5011b24\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180606%2F58283141&h=1ba23afa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180606/58283141</a>"},{"pid":"60f4d46fd63599a495660e1d3a7fd44987d443b7","tid":691884,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T06:42:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10549a9781aae88803016d9de4c1f8229a67f559","tid":691884,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T06:43:27.000Z","msg":"郵寄地址，要求<span style=\"color: red;\">信封</span>註明「游蕙禎收」。有關訊息亦有人代為轉貼在游的fb。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHK No IT<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cdf2466e7bac833908d1d87ddad8adec5446ef9","tid":691884,"uid":54870,"like":0,"